        "### 1. Auth0 Token Vault Integration (Simulated)\n",
        "In a production scenario, Auth0 for AI Agents provides a secure identity layer where the agent fetches the access token on behalf of the user to access external APIs. Here, we simulate that step to retrieve our Kaggle API credentials."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 3,
      "id": "91e8c3fe",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "91e8c3fe",
        "outputId": "edd39528-88b0-47a9-ba8a-7fb13d5b6f92"
      },
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "[Auth0 Vault] Real Kaggle Credentials injected into environment.\n"
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import requests\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_kaggle_credentials_via_vault():\n",
