        " media\\\" alt=\\\"\\\"></p>\\n<p><a href=\\\"https://www.sbert.net/docs/package_reference/losses.html#megabatchmarginloss\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">MegaBatchMarginLoss</a> was chosen as loss function, \n",
